title: Log in to use the Notification of Vehicle Arrivals (NOVA) service

heading_context: Log in to use the Notification of Vehicle Arrivals (NOVA) service
chunks.html_content:
Use the NOVA service to tell HM Revenue and Customs (HMRC) you’ve brought a vehicle into the UK.

You can use the service if:

  • you’re a VAT-registered business that does not use the secure registration scheme
  • you’re not VAT-registered and you’ve imported a vehicle from the EU into Northern Ireland

heading_context: Log in to use the Notification of Vehicle Arrivals (NOVA) service
chunks.html_content: To use this service you need a Government Gateway user ID and password. If you do not have a user ID, you can create one when you use the service.
